# terraform/.env — copy this to terraform/.env and fill in the values
# This file is gitignored. Never commit terraform/.env with real credentials.
#
# Usage: all terraform commands should be run via the Makefile:
#   make apply
#   make destroy
#   make plan
#
# These automatically load this file so you never need to export manually.

# ── Arize AX tracing ──────────────────────────────────────────
